{"tid":1006825,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【跨性別覆核案敗訴】跨仔Henry真名告政府：只想香港承認自己","createTime":"2019-02-03T09:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T12:21:54.000Z","uid":109780,"like":6,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"88f001e7ed3600492304f8abcba5fa9ee289557d","tid":1006825,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PBTbREH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPBTbREH.jpg&h=4b3ddc4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跨男司法覆核案，高等法院今日宣佈未完成整項性別重置手術的人士，不可獲更改香港身份證的性別。案中唯一不用化名入稟的申請人謝浩霖（Henry Edward Tse），2017年與另外兩名同樣由女變男的「跨仔」Q和R，入稟法院提出司法覆核入境處的決定。三人去年初聆訊後，等候裁決結果逾一年。Henry在裁決前接受《香港01》專訪，談人權法，也談起自己如何走上這性別平權的路。<br />\n<br />\nHenry原生性別為女性，自我認同為男性，七年前在英國留學時求醫，服用男性荷爾蒙藥物並切去乳房，2016年獲英國的性別承認證書，以男性身份於當地擁有法律權利。當初留在英國便能安然生活工作，為什麼他還要回來這個仍沒有「性別承認法」的香港？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0KZf6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0KZf6G.jpg&h=f1e4f2ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n型過9成連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/276072/%E8%B7%A8%E6%80%A7%E5%88%A5%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E6%A1%88%E6%95%97%E8%A8%B4-%E8%B7%A8%E4%BB%94henry%E7%9C%9F%E5%90%8D%E5%91%8A%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E5%8F%AA%E6%83%B3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C%2F276072%2F%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%2588%25A5%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%2595%2597%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E4%25BB%2594henry%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA